title: Space Trek 3016
description: Join the crew of the starship Engager as they explore the galaxy and face off with the Klamulons.
quote: I’m no human. I am Lieutenant Tork of the planet Mars. And you’ve never encountered anything like me before.
altHero: Captain Tom Bender and Lieutenant Tork on the bridge of the ship
alt1: Tork shapeshifted into a gorilla fights some Klamulons
alt2: Tork and Ensign Valiant beam up into the ship
alt3: Klamulon points a laser gun at Captain Bender
alt4: Tork shoots a laser gun from behind a rock
